### Recommend — raw text
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/recommend
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

candidate_name=Rahul Sharma&raw_text=Rahul Sharma. Python developer with 2 years of ML and NLP experience. Skills: Python TensorFlow Scikit-learn NLP SQL Pandas Hugging Face BERT. Education: B.Tech Computer Science NIT Trichy 2024 CGPA 8.6. Experience: Data Science Intern at Flipkart May 2023 Aug 2023. Built recommendation system using collaborative filtering. Certifications: DeepLearning.AI TensorFlow Developer.

